{"compress":true,"commitItems":[["6105176c-3261-4de6-9893-ea798c08ef2f",1536631448642,"",[[1536631410845,["pljhonglu@Honglu-Macbook-Pro.local",[[1,0,"# [安全日记] - 一\n\n\n\n"]],[0,0],[15,15]]],[1536631413032,["pljhonglu@Honglu-Macbook-Pro.local",[[1,15,"这种攻击方式称为“同形异义词”攻击。其实并不是新方法，最早能追溯到2001年。不过由于一些现实情况，该问题目前依然存在于不少浏览器。\n\n它的原理是这样的：有些国家或地区的网站域名会用到一些“地方语言”，比如希腊、西里尔、亚美尼亚，这些网址看起来虽然一样，但是电脑却认为不同。例如：\n\n这里有三个看起来差不多的字符 ：ａ、a、α ，但是第一个是西里尔文的 ａ，第二个是英文里的 a、第三个是俄文里的 α （数学题里的阿尔法）\n\n虽然看起来都是 A，但计算机显然把它们当成不同的字符来对待。"]],[15,15],[258,258]]],[1536631419588,["pljhonglu@Honglu-Macbook-Pro.local",[[1,14,"## 同形异义词"]],[14,14],[22,22]]],[1536631420148,["pljhonglu@Honglu-Macbook-Pro.local",[[1,23,"\n"]],[22,22],[23,23]]],[1536631433639,["pljhonglu@Honglu-Macbook-Pro.local",[[1,23,"[图片]"]],[23,23],[27,27]]],[1536631442163,["pljhonglu@Honglu-Macbook-Pro.local",[[-1,23,"[图片]"]],[27,27],[23,23]]],[1536631445619,["pljhonglu@Honglu-Macbook-Pro.local",[[1,24,"\n"]],[23,23],[24,24]]],[1536631447060,["pljhonglu@Honglu-Macbook-Pro.local",[[1,25,"\n"]],[23,23],[24,24]]],[1536631493218,["pljhonglu@Honglu-Macbook-Pro.local",[[1,24,"![CE4C1F7344ED60531A6EBEF484FFC395]($resource/CE4C1F7344ED60531A6EBEF484FFC395.jpg)"]],[24,24],[108,108]]],[1536631499301,["pljhonglu@Honglu-Macbook-Pro.local",[[-1,108,"\n"]],[108,108],[107,107]]],[1536631500781,["pljhonglu@Honglu-Macbook-Pro.local",[[1,108,"\n"]],[107,107],[108,108]]],[1536631500791,["pljhonglu@Honglu-Macbook-Pro.local",[[1,108,"、"]],[108,108],[109,109]]],[1536631501856,["pljhonglu@Honglu-Macbook-Pro.local",[[-1,108,"、"]],[109,109],[108,108]]],[1536631596986,["pljhonglu@Honglu-Macbook-Pro.local",[[1,22,"攻击"]],[22,22],[24,24]]]],null,"pljhonglu@Honglu-Macbook-Pro.local"]]}